{"title":"Convert letters to lowercase","description":"Convert all letters in the text from uppercase to lowercase, or change all uppercase letters to lowercase for the whole text or part of it.","content":"## Convert all letters to lowercase\r\nThis tool allows you to convert all letters in the text from uppercase to lowercase or change all uppercase letters to lowercase. \r\nA change to lowercase for the whole text or part of it may be necessary to convert the text to the correct form, in which all letters are lowercase, excluding the first letter of the first word in the sentence, proper words or other variants, depending on the language and the rules established in it.\n\n You can also familiarize yourself with other functionality of this online [text editor](/en/editor)."}